   <name>AloxBook</name>
   <summary>Privacy-first personal double-entry bookkeeping</summary>
   <description>
      <p>
         AloxBook is a personal finance application that brings real double-entry
         bookkeeping to your desktop. It is fast to learn, quick to use, and your
         data stays entirely on your machine in encrypted local storage.
      </p>
      <p>
         Features include a hierarchical account tree, CSV import with configurable
         profiles, transaction templates, period close and carry forward, and full
         English, German and French language support with live switching.
      </p>
   </description>
   <developer id="com.aloxbook">
